---
title: Asian Stir-Fried Chicken & Nutty Garlic Rice with Oyster Sauce Broccoli & Sesame Dressing
description: Pan-fried chicken and stir-fried veggies; it’s almost too good to be true. Cook the veggies in a umami oyster sauce and sprinkle on the delicious combination of sweet and soy over the chicken. This will help to give it a signature golden glow. ! Even the rice has an extra kick of flavour from the nutty garlic. This dinner really is a dream come true!
